\par \pard\plain \s6\sa120 \f2\fs20\lang1033 If this boolean {\uldb variable}{\v Variables} is set to TRUE, the echoing of input at the command prompts is enabled.
\par \pard \s6\sa120 Default value: TRUE.
\par \pard\plain \s251\sa120\tx2880 \b\f2\fs20\lang1033 \page {\plain \f2\fs16\up6\lang1033 ${\footnote \pard\plain \s245 \f2\fs20\lang1033 {\fs16\up6 $} $disphigh variable}} {\plain \f2\fs16\up6\lang1033 #{\footnote \pard\plain \s245 \f2\fs20\lang1033 {
